OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FGranada Reports Sports Correspondent
OL,7,FDavid Chisnall reports on Guardiola's
OL,8,Fextraordinary decade-long reign
OL,10,FManchester City have confirmed that
OL,11,FPep Guardiola will leave the club
OL,12,Fafter ten years in charge.
OL,14,FHis decade-long reign at City is one
OL,15,Fof the most successful managerial
OL,16,Fspells in English football history,
OL,17,Fhaving won 20 trophies, including six
OL,18,FPremier League titles and the
OL,19,FChampions League.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
