CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FFor months, Guardiola - who will go
OL,7,Fdown as one of the finest managers to
OL,8,Fgrace English football - had continued
OL,9,Fto insist he had "one more year" left
OL,10,Fon his contract.
OL,12,FBut today, Manchester City announced
OL,13,Fhis departure on X, with the caption:
OL,14,F"What a time we have had together."
OL,16,FThe Catalan became the club's greatest
OL,17,Fever signing in 2016, when the most
OL,18,Fsought-after coach in world football
OL,19,Fjoined as manager.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FHis possession-based, attacking style
OL,7,Fof play brought trophies galore at
OL,8,FBarcelona and Bayern Munich, and his
OL,9,Fchallenge was to replicate that in
OL,10,FEnglish football. But his first season
OL,11,Fwas trophyless and his tactics were
OL,12,Fquestioned.
OL,14,FDoubters were soon proven wrong after
OL,15,FGuardiola secured his first silverware
OL,16,Fat City with a 3-0 win over Arsenal in
OL,17,Fthe Carabao Cup final in 2018.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FAt the time, the manager said: "It's
OL,7,Fspecial, Sergio, Vincent and David
OL,8,Fscoring the three goals. They help us
OL,9,Fto understand what it means in the
OL,10,Fclub. The people coming here they have
OL,11,Fto know here you have to win titles."
OL,13,FCity went on to win the league title
OL,14,Fin style with a record 100 points,
OL,15,Freaching the century thanks to a
OL,16,Fstoppage-time winner from Gabriel
OL,17,FJesus at Southampton on the final day.
OL,19,FFrom there, more records were broken
OL,20,Fas more trophies were lifted.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
