OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FThe following season City became the
OL,7,Ffirst English team to do the domestic
OL,8,Ftreble, winning the League Cup, the FA
OL,9,FCup and pipping Liverpool to the
OL,10,FPremier League title by a single point.
OL,12,FThe battle between Guardiola's City
OL,13,Fand Jurgen Klopp's Liverpool would
OL,14,Fbecame one of the greatest rivalries
OL,15,Fin English football and define that
OL,16,Fera of Premier League history.
OL,18,FKlopp said at the time: "Pep is the
OL,19,Fbest manager in the world. I know I'm
OL,20,Fnot bad but you asked me about the
OL,21,Fbest and for me he's the best."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FGuardiola's incredible record saw him
OL,7,Fguide City to six Premier League
OL,8,Ftitles in seven years.
OL,10,FAs the dominant force in England,
OL,11,FGuardiola finally conquered Europe
OL,12,Fwith City in 2023. His team beat Inter
OL,13,FMilan in the Champions League final in
OL,14,FIstanbul to complete a historic treble
OL,15,Fand match the achievements of Sir Alex
OL,16,FFerguson's Manchester United side of
OL,17,F1999.
OL,19,FPep said: "It's an honour for me to be
OL,20,Falongside Sir Alex Ferguson in that
OL,21,Fsituation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,F"I got a message from him this morning
OL,7,Fin my phone that touched me a lot. You
OL,8,Fhave to win Europe to be considered
OL,9,Fone of the really good good teams and
OL,10,Fwe did it."
OL,12,FThe UEFA Super Cup and FIFA Club World
OL,13,FCup both followed that year. But for
OL,14,Fall the success, Guardiola once joked
OL,15,Fit couldn't make up for the fact that
OL,16,Fone of his heroes is a fan of City's
OL,17,Fneighbour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FHe said: "I have three idols in my
OL,7,Flife, Michael Jordan, Tiger Woods and
OL,8,FJulia Roberts. So Julia Roberts years
OL,9,Fago came to Manchester and she went to
OL,10,Fsee Manchester United she didn't come
OL,11,Fto see us.
OL,13,F"Even if I win the Champions League it
OL,14,Fwill not compare to the fact that
OL,15,FJulia Roberts came to Manchester and
OL,16,Fdidn't come to see us."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FThe trophies continued, as City became
OL,7,Fthe first to win four Premier Leagues
OL,8,Fin a row between 2021 and 2024. But
OL,9,FGuardiola's reign has coincided with
OL,10,Fmany challenges.
OL,12,FIt was referred to an independent
OL,13,Fcommission in respect of a series of
OL,14,Falleged breaches of rules related to
OL,15,Fclub finances in 2023. The outcome of
OL,16,Fthe investigation is still pending,
OL,17,Fbut City could face a hefty points
OL,18,Fdeduction or even expulsion from the
OL,19,Fleague if found guilty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
