FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779628274
OL,3,CPep Guardiola to leave Manchester City
OL,4,Cafter ten years in charge
OL,6,FAfter a fourth successive Premier
OL,7,FLeague title in 2024, defeat by
OL,8,FCrystal Palace in the FA Cup final
OL,9,Fmeant the Community Shield was their
OL,10,Fonly silverware the following season.
OL,12,FThis season, Guardiola bows out with
OL,13,Ftwo more trophies after Wembley
OL,14,Fvictories over Arsenal and Chelsea in
OL,15,Fthe League Cup and FA Cup finals,
OL,16,Frespectively.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
